snippet.textDisplay:
When I watch this, watch this video, watch this man, I realise what the haters are talking about. To anyone who isn’t a Liverpool fan reading this, not all Liverpool supporters are this arrogant. And you keep referring to the lads as kids, they are young professionals who represent Liverpool, the club we love, I am sure you mean no disrespect to the youngsters, but you do give that impression. We won, the youngsters did it, I’m very proud of them, on to the fourth round we go. And unlucky to Everton, they didn’t perform and they will be disappointed with themselves. Bitterness makes football ugly. Football is a beautiful sport.

Disclaimer: I did not watch all of the video as I didn’t want to, so I apologise to the presenter personally if I was wrong in what I said.
snippet.textOriginal:
When I watch this, watch this video, watch this man, I realise what the haters are talking about. To anyone who isn’t a Liverpool fan reading this, not all Liverpool supporters are this arrogant. And you keep referring to the lads as kids, they are young professionals who represent Liverpool, the club we love, I am sure you mean no disrespect to the youngsters, but you do give that impression. We won, the youngsters did it, I’m very proud of them, on to the fourth round we go. And unlucky to Everton, they didn’t perform and they will be disappointed with themselves. Bitterness makes football ugly. Football is a beautiful sport.

Disclaimer: I did not watch all of the video as I didn’t want to, so I apologise to the presenter personally if I was wrong in what I said.
